<!-- Button trigger modal -->
<button type="button" class="a-btn" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#modalExample">
  Launch demo modal
</button>


<!-- Modal -->
<div class="modal a-modal fade" id="modalExample" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg" role="document">

    <!-- Modal Top -->
    <div class="a-modal-top">
      <img id="altinnlogo" class="a-modal-top-logo" src="../../images/a-logo-white.svg">

      <div id="represented-by-user" class="a-modal-top-user hidden-xs">

        <i class="material-icons a-modal-top-user-icon">person</i>

          <span class="a-modal-top-user-name">
            STEPHAN ISDAHL
          </span>
      </div>

      <div class="a-modal-navbar">

        <button type="button" class="a-modal-back" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Lukk">
          <i class="material-icons a-modal-back-icon">keyboard_backspace</i>
        </button>

        <button type="button" class="a-modal-close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Lukk">
          <i class="material-icons a-modal-close-icon">close</i>
        </button>


      </div>
    </div>


    <!-- Modal content -->
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header a-modal-header">

        <i class="material-icons a-collapse-icon">devices</i>
        <h2 class="modal-title a-modal-title" id="myModalLabel">How to use the design system</h2>

      </div>
      <div class="modal-body a-modal-body a-text">
        <p>Atomic design is a methodology used to construct web design systems. Read more about it <a href="http://localhost:3000/?p=all">here</a>. You can find all the components in the top navigation bar, organized into Atoms, Molecules, Organisms, Templates and Pages. </p>
        <hr>
        <h3 class="headerSmall">Keyboard Shortcuts</h3>
        <b>ctrl+shift+a:</b> open/close annotations view <br>
      <b>ctrl+shift+c:</b> open/close code view</p><br>
      <h3 class="headerSmall">The goal</h3>
      <p>The goals for us in creating this type of living Design System are:
        <ul>
          <li>Maintain a consistency of styles and identity in all Alltinn's web solutions</li>
          <li>Having one common prototype environment where we are simultaneously able to see components abstractly and in context</li>
          <li>Streamline the workflow for designers and developers</li>
          <li>Create a focal point for our Design and User Experience work, both for ourselves and for the community</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      {{> atoms-itemlist }}



      <div class="modal-footer">

        <div class="a-btn-group">

          {{# ButtonLink }}
              {{> atoms-link-standalone }}
          {{/ ButtonLink }}

          {{# ButtonLink }}
              {{> atoms-link-button }}
          {{/ ButtonLink }}

        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
